Nechci

16
00:02:19,101 --> 00:02:19,740
sladké.

17
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:23,020
Pak...

18
00:02:24,044 --> 00:02:25,344
co ti mám objednat?

19
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:27,980
Jenom čaj.

20
00:02:41,804 --> 00:02:44,504
